<br>
There's a second movie coming out called Innocence which is a sequel to the movie version.<br>
<br>
Stand Alone Complex is an alternate version of the original, and yeah, if you haven't read the manga...go read it now! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
Much different from the movie in mood. If you've seen the series, it's much more like that.<br>
