<br>
In some ways the movie is a retelling of Little Red Riding Hood. With guns, armor, intrigue, explosions, etc.<br>
To say too much would be a spoiler, but essentially it revolves around internal affairs and the effort to preserve a pseudo-military organization now that it's not needed. The setting is actually more of an alternate post-WWII Japan than the futuristic world of GiTS.<br>
Like the GiTS movie, it can be a little slow at times (though I think the pacing is more consistent), however, it's rewarding for those with patience. It's not too hard to find, I've even seen it at Wal Mart. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=onigawa>Onigawa</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://kfc.sapphiresky.org/bbs/images/avatars/6932122083f1f984dcd0b9.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(8/19/03 7:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2480.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://kfc.sapphiresky.org/bbs/images/avatars/6932122083f1f984dcd0b9.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_lightbulb.gif" align=absmiddle>  jin-roh</span><hr size=1> Thanx....but I don't think Malaysia has a Wal-Mart. but thanx anyway, I'll hunt it down and proudly watch it at home.....have you seen Techi Muyo...what do you think??..and has anyone seen spirggan...what does anyone thinK??? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=themightyservo>The Mighty Servo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(8/20/03 5:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2480.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://filebox.vt.edu/users/cmayer/images/servo.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_lightbulb.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: